{"tid":495829,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"牙齒浸可樂 14天斷兩截  僅兩天染咖啡色","createTime":"2017-12-11T06:02:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T06:24:21.000Z","uid":10958,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b9b028c5629e2df9fdb6b72a90968144edb4b90d","tid":495829,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T06:02:21.000Z","msg":"<strong>牙齒浸可樂 14天斷兩截  僅兩天染咖啡色</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1965000/1966819/11JIB008__20171211_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1965000%2F1966819%2F11JIB008__20171211_L.jpg&h=6ea4423b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">牙齒酸蝕問題成都市人常見牙患，尤其喜歡飲汽水最易出事。</span><br />\n<br />\n碳酸飲料對牙齒可造成嚴重傷害，英國一項實驗測試7款飲料對人類牙齒的損害程度，結果顯示潔白的牙齒浸在可樂兩天後已變咖啡色，兩周後更斷成兩截。<br />\n<br />\n英國口腔健康協會近日測試了7款飲料對人類牙齒的損害程度，他們將牙齒浸泡在7項飲料中14日，持續觀察牙齒的變化，其中包括意大利葡萄氣泡酒Prosecco、蘋果酒、可樂、能量飲料、運動飲料、牛奶及清水。<br />\n<br />\n結果發現，可樂、意大利葡萄氣泡酒及蘋果酒對牙齒的損害最為驚人。當中蘋果酒中的酸性讓牙齒的琺瑯質嚴重脫鈣，使象牙質變得清晰可見；葡萄氣泡酒中大量的糖分和氣泡不斷侵蝕琺瑯質，導致牙齒化成粉末狀的碎屑；至於浸在可樂的牙齒，僅兩天就嚴重染色，並且琺瑯質因鈣質大量流失變得十分脆弱，14天後完全斷裂。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>運動能量飲料亦有害</strong><br />\n<br />\n此外，能量飲料和運動飲料雖不如碳酸飲料侵蝕力般嚴重，但因酸含量相對較高，加上高量糖份，亦很快損害牙齒，浸於能量飲品兩周的牙齒表面由光滑變得凹凸不平，而運動飲品則令牙齒顏色變成灰白，顯示琺瑯質鈣質開始流失。<br />\n<br />\n至於牛奶和清水屬於中性酸鹼度水平，亦不含糖分，故不對牙齒造成傷害。<br />\n<br />\n專家阿特金斯指這些飲料酸度高及糖分多，能快速侵蝕牙齒，呼籲大眾減少飲用︰「我們每喝一口含糖飲料，我們口中的細菌就會以糖為食，因而產生牙菌斑，至於酸性物質則會不斷侵蝕琺瑯質。」他補充若實驗中牙齒受損的情況發生在人身上，將帶來劇痛，牙齒更有可能被拔除。<br />\n<br />\n編輯︰吳浩南<br />\n<br />\n美術︰李明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1965000/1966819/028_01_a_20171211_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1965000%2F1966819%2F028_01_a_20171211_L.jpg&h=da24f193&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">潔白的牙齒浸可樂兩天已變咖啡色。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1965000/1966819/028_01_b_20171211_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1965000%2F1966819%2F028_01_b_20171211_L.jpg&h=7972773a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1966819/%E7%89%99%E9%BD%92%E6%B5%B8%E5%8F%AF%E6%A8%82%2014%E5%A4%A9%E6%96%B7%E5%85%A9%E6%88%AA/?ref=fb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1966819%2F%25E7%2589%2599%25E9%25BD%2592%25E6%25B5%25B8%25E5%258F%25AF%25E6%25A8%2582%252014%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%2596%25B7%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%2588%25AA%2F%3Fref%3Dfb&d=K3Mti2WBIh1zTkKWbeZO7JzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=0ee9a59d\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1966819/%E7%89%99%E9%BD%92%E6%B5%B8%E5%8F%AF%E6%A8%82%2014%E5%A4%A9%E6%96%B7%E5%85%A9%E6%88%AA/?ref=fb</a>"},{"pid":"08ba4b921f1c99dcd717e5bb41609014947d417f","tid":495829,"uid":108467,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T06:04:39.000Z","msg":"英國研究😂"},{"pid":"787fdcf98da9a7091338c6d15f4f8aa56b0dc10f","tid":495829,"uid":41116,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T06:05:58.000Z","msg":"你含啖可樂含兩日？"},{"pid":"88fdaca3f443c5ce51ede184368184ba4bce671b","tid":495829,"uid":40179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T06:07:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你含啖可樂含兩日？</blockquote><br />\n職業病掛..."},{"pid":"5c4414a621381ee2d27f7676c6147d4efe6d5686","tid":495829,"uid":726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T06:07:24.000Z","msg":"溝埋口水話唔定可樂最有益"},{"pid":"72a8149a6076db08ded8ce2c9f51a32d9df56aca","tid":495829,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T06:13:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你含啖可樂含兩日？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 